name: Office Building
description: This is my second single player map. My VERY first single player map has been lost in the abyss forever, but I did make a mock up, which I hope to upload shortly after this one. This Office Building map, I hope you enjoy because I did put an extra touch in because this was originally done in 2011 but never finished until now. I did my best to keep it as simple as I could do it in 2011 with some techniques I have learned in the past 7 years, but not too many.
